  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/5ff759f6ff4d608a348592f9b5fdc01c.avif?t=1762882607\" width=610 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daemonium is a 1-4 player online co-op psychological horror game. Demonic possessions are running rampant. Grab your equipment, join your team, and locate the source of the demonic presence. Enter the portal to the demon realm to stop the possession once and for all. Perform an exorcism and banish the entity to hell before it claims your soul.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>- \"One of the best rituals in any ghost hunting game\"</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/1f8e7b92daf23d1144ba47a3611e141c.avif?t=1762882607\" width=487 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players can play in a wide variety of locations as well as a selection of demon realms which are chosen randomly each game</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/ba9ebcdf7becdccc7c51104346d822e2.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/ba9ebcdf7becdccc7c51104346d822e2.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/ba9ebcdf7becdccc7c51104346d822e2.mp4?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/e780ad9b3595fd1a1f5332f006195061.avif?t=1762882607\" width=487 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Play together with up to 4 player teams</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/858fb28fafa560486e92ce1a3809b876.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=614 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/858fb28fafa560486e92ce1a3809b876.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/858fb28fafa560486e92ce1a3809b876.mp4?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/1cf7108bec0125e38baa34fcf6dacd11.avif?t=1762882607\" width=487 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a wide range of equipment to find evidence of paranormal activity and reveal the possessed item<br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/8adf631dbf701eb79ab38d7431693d99.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/8adf631dbf701eb79ab38d7431693d99.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/8adf631dbf701eb79ab38d7431693d99.mp4?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/1c57e731e6e41637ed9b62cda8eaaf47.avif?t=1762882607\" width=503 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remove possessed items from the locations</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/fa91e8eefba1dbbf6dc698b2cc3e9510.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/fa91e8eefba1dbbf6dc698b2cc3e9510.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/fa91e8eefba1dbbf6dc698b2cc3e9510.mp4?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/b2b62fcd8c22ebbf7c760c8e42025229.avif?t=1762882607\" width=552 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enter the demon realm at your peril</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/d08711b462f85acd734db0cf62301266.poster.avif?t=1762882607\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2327140/extras/d08711b462f85acd734db0cf62301266.webm?t=1762882607\" type=\"video/webm; codec